{"tid":492250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[腳膠轉世]婦蜜月遊泰 怪蟲鑽腳掌","createTime":"2017-12-07T10:51:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T07:42:56.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1930a325c804d3383627b032e2da0c8a0afedce4","tid":492250,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:51:32.000Z","msg":"泰國憑着陽光與海灘成為旅遊勝地，但因位處熱帶地區，昆蟲極多，而暗藏危機。近日，遼寧大連一對新婚夫婦到泰國度蜜月，惟該名年輕新娘回國後竟發現腳底皮膚出現一條彎曲的紅線，且又痛又癢；到醫院經檢查後，她原來是被活蟲鑽進腳底，所幸接受液態氮冷凍治療後，活蟲已被凍死。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20171207/photo/1207-00178-027b1.jpg?t=1512643862179\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20171207%2Fphoto%2F1207-00178-027b1.jpg%3Ft%3D1512643862179&h=29dd1baa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20171207/00178_027.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20171207%2F00178_027.html&d=RAgTfSvKuYoXmTgMV7u6nm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=e8ff87ef\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20171207/00178_027.html</a>"},{"pid":"3c0494ca9037b101b570d5fb4310d9ddfa2181f2","tid":492250,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:51:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898362d8ce9a7d60bffce5de4f4d7096cb69378b","tid":492250,"uid":143183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:54:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4645dd520ca5f28784d5995005c24b41aa10352","tid":492250,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T10:55:55.000Z","msg